This paper deals with security and privacy in computer systems, which falls under the category of "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the development of a theory and algorithms for analyzing the security of systems, which could be categorized under "cs.LO" (Logic in Computer Science) and "cs.PL" (Programming Languages). The paper also deals with the application of different security policies in different parts of a system, which could be categorized under "cs.SE" (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper involves the development of complexity results, which could be categorized under "cs.FL" (Formal Languages and Automata Theory).
